      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/feds-schmid-no-need-preemptively-cut-rates-2024-02-27/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[堪萨斯城联邦储备银行行长杰弗里·施密德周一在首次政策演讲中表示，他仍然关注高通胀的威胁，并不急于降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/feds-schmid-no-need-preemptively-cut-rates-2024-02-27/</guid>
